moved on to the tchaikovsky symphony he finished the main concert 
with the wildly varying emotions and styles of the symphony no 5 
of dmitri shostakovich whose grave he had visited immediately on 
arrival in moscow 
after five bows to cries of bravo and tumultuous applause 
rostropovich moved into an encore of a brief shostakovich polka 
and was drawn back for three more encores 
