the airbus 320 crashed at 1 pm while on final approach to the 
runway at bangalore airport airline and airport officials said 
the crash occurred before the plane touched the runway and it 
caught fire as soon as it crashed said ps shetty airport 
manager in bombay where the hourlong flight had originated 
