indian airlines the major domestic carrier flies to 73 cities 
nationwide and to nine nearby countries it has come under 
criticism for allegedly failing to maintain preflight safety 
procedures on its fleet and to adequately supervise its pilots 
delays in flight schedules also are endemic 
