of course its an unusual situation because there are in 
colombia these guerrilla bands terrorist bands with access to 
funds to purchase on the open market any kinds of arms and so 
naturally there are unusual circumstances scowcroft said tuesday 
at a white house briefing 
but we think theyre adequately taken care of he added 
the main purpose of bushs attendance at the summit is a show of 
us support for drugfighting efforts in the three andean 
drugproducing nations plus the expected issuance of a joint 
communique vowing an increased effort to fight the problem 
