noble a graduate of bristol university has been an associate 
director of the company for 11 years staging such admired 
productions as henry v which marked the professional 
shakespearean debut of this years oscar nominee kenneth branagh 
henrik ibsens the master builder with broadway veteran john 
wood and a trilogy the plantagenets drawn from four 
shakespeare history plays 
his 1987 revival of cole porters kiss me kate drew mixed 
reviews but transferred to the commercial west end for a lengthy 
run a mooted broadway engagement never materialized 
noble made his american directing debut last december in new 
york earning excellent reviews for the art of success 
offbroadway at the manhattan theater club 
next he stages chekhovs three sisters for the gate theater 
in dublin opening march 27 the production a dynastic occasion 
will star leading irish actor cyril cusack and three of his four 
actress daughters sorcha sinead and niamh 
