radionuclides isotopes for medicine and biology for the northern 
hemisphere maybe north and south 
i think there is going to be a shuffling and hopefully there 
will be provisions made said goldsmith they probably have 
supplies for a week of the shortlived material 
in a letter to company officials the nrc acknowledged the 
effects the suspension could have on nuclear medicine said nrc 
spokesman steve horwitz 
therefore please keep the regional administrator informed of 
the impact of this order on the ability of the medical community to 
obtain radioisotopes the letter said 
all of the leaks were contained and none allowed radioactive 
material to reach the nearby indian kill reservoir which serves 
more than 100 households company officials said 
the latest leak was found in a water tank that is part of the 
