manager james j mcgovern 
the shutdown order requires cintichem to determine causes of the 
leaks and check for equipment breakdowns show how repairs will be 
done and prove that they will hold and put together a monitoring 
program to assure prompt detection of future leaks 
in addition the state dec intends to delay approval of 
cintichems air emissions and drainage runoff discharge permits 
